      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superb opportunity for the driver-centric enthusiast. At its heart lies the S54 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for razor-sharp throttle response. Power is delivered through a high-engagement limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal corner-exit traction. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS service. While the exterior shows minor signs of road use, the mechanical vitals are robust and the suspension geometry remains true. A well-sorted, high-performance icon ready for the canyons.",
