      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, offering a seamless blend of performance and reliability. The exterior maintains a lustrous finish, showing only the minor, negligible signs of careful road use typical of a well-loved car. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats are firm and supportive with no significant wear, and the dashboard remains free of any sun damage or blemishes. Every feature, from the responsive infotainment system to the crisp air conditioning, operates perfectly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, backed by a consistent maintenance record that ensures peace of mind for the next owner. It has recently undergone a full multi-point inspection and comes with tires that have plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, dependable choice for anyone seeking a vehicle that looks great and drives even better.",
